beer.beer_description:
We're not sure why we didn't start down the road of imperial stouts a while ago, but the rabbit hole is deep with a few obligatory combos on the way down.
✅ - Salted Caramel
✅ - Coffee
And now
✅ - Maple
Would you believe we had to buy our local supplier out of maple syrup for this one?

See can copy for Charlie's amazing poem.

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 230 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 47!

items.checkin_comment:
Jet black appearance with an inviting head. Aromas of maple syrup - you can tell this one is rich, even before tasting!
